; Coverage for compare.cc: date comparison in sort

2024/01/15 Second
    Expenses:Food    $20.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/01 First
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg Expenses --sort date
24-Jan-01 First                 Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
24-Jan-15 Second                Expenses:Food                $20.00       $30.00
end test
